<html ><head ><meta charset="UTF-8"  /><meta name="author" content="Martin Walther - @tinuwalther"  /><meta name="keywords" content="Pode, PSHTML, PowerShell, Mermaid Diagram"  /><meta name="description" content="Builds beatuifull HTML-Files with PSHTML from native PowerShell-Scripts"  /><link href="\assets\BootStrap\bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"  /><link href="\assets\style\style.css" rel="stylesheet"  /><script src="\assets\BootStrap\bootstrap.bundle.min.js"  ></script><title >#PSXi Help</title><link type="image/x-icon" rel="icon" href="/assets/img/favicon.ico"  /></head><Body ><header ><div Style="padding:15; background-color:#033b63" Id="j1" Class="jumbotron text-center"  ><p ><h1 >#PSXi Help</h1></p><p >I ♥ PS Pode > This is an example for using pode and PSHTML, requested by API</p></div></header><Section Id="section"  ><nav Class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark sticky-top"  ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><a href="/" Class="navbar-brand" Target="_self"  >»HOME</a><button Class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar"  ><span Class="navbar-toggler-icon"  ></span></button><div Id="collapsibleNavbar" Class="collapse navbar-collapse"  ><ul Class="navbar-nav"  ><li Class="nav-item"  ><a href="#RebuildByFW" Class="nav-link" Target="_self"  >Re-build by FileWatcher</a></li><li Class="nav-item"  ><a href="#RebuildByAPI" Class="nav-link" Target="_self"  >Re-build by API</a></li></ul></div></div></nav><div Id="Content" Class="Container"  ><article Id="Pode"  ><h1 Style="color:#212529"  >Re-build pages</h1><h2 Style="color:#212529" Id="RebuildByAPI"  >Re-build by API</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Index.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/index -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pode-Server.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/pode -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Update-Assets.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/asset -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the SQLite-Data.pode page with own sql query:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/sqlite -Method Post -Body 'SELECT * FROM "classic_ESXiHosts" Limit 7'</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pester-Result.pode page with own destinations to test:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/pester -Method Post -Body '["sbb.ch","admin.ch"]'</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Mermaid-Diagram.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/mermaid -Method Post -Body 'SELECT * FROM "classic_ESXiHosts" ORDER BY HostName'</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Help.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/help -Method Post</pre></article></div></Section><pre Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the page: I ♥ PS > Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/help -Method Post</pre></Body><div Style="background-color:#343a40" Class="container-fluid"  ><footer ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><div Class="row align-items-center"  ><div Class="col-md"  ><p ><a href="#" Class="btn-sm btn btn-outline-success" Target="_self"  >I ♥ PS ></a></p></div><div Class="col-md"  ><p >Based on <a href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/Pode" Target="_blank"  >pode</a> and <a href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/PSHTML" Target="_blank"  >PSHTML</a></p></div><div Style="color:#000" Class="col-md"  ><p >Created at 2024-07-18 18:32:48</p></div></div></div></footer></div></html>
